{"tid":1017086,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[BTS又贏] BTS防彈少年團登上Grammy Awards葛萊美！RM承諾：我們會再回來","createTime":"2019-02-11T08:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:23:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd5ca40fb125335f1cfa6e3f2e336de01d2b8bc","tid":1017086,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"西洋樂壇一年一度盛事「第61屆葛萊美獎」於美國時間10日晚間（台灣時間11日上午9點）舉行，韓團防彈少年團（BTS）以頒獎人身份首次出席盛會，他們頒發「最佳R&amp;B專輯獎」。七名成員穿著帥氣西裝上台，隊長RM承諾：「我們會再回來！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888625.jpg&h=feac0c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「第61屆葛萊美獎」防彈少年團登台頒獎，隊長RM承諾「會再回來」。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團以頒獎人身份出席，隊長RM在站上葛萊美舞台時，感性表示：「我們在韓國長大，一直夢想可以來到葛萊美，謝謝所有的粉絲。」並強調：「我們會再回來！」隨後揭曉獎項，將大獎頒給年僅21歲的女歌手H.E.R。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888623.jpg&h=38c305e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「第61屆葛萊美獎」防彈少年團登台。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888624.jpg&h=32060cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲H.E.R從防彈少年團手的V手中接下獎座。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\nH.E.R以同名《H.E.R.》獲獎，她露出驚訝的表情，上台從防彈少年團手的V手中接下獎座。H.E.R驚喜地說道：「這甚至只是一張EP而不是專輯，我希望我的團隊都可以一起上來，這些事情不是我一人，而是我們一起完成的。」她也感動表示：「我要忍住不哭，謝謝我的家人對我的犧牲， 我三歲就跟RCA簽約，謝謝他們相信我。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888622.jpg&h=f4690578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團是第一組參加葛萊美獎的南韓歌手。（圖／CFP）"},{"pid":"bbd8e8f3f0b041e931b067c36d26c89855193603","tid":1017086,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"Grammy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1fb0c8820248941905805c9fc1a895aa0f6fd9","tid":1017086,"uid":194877,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"R乜M 以為running man<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed677368b5b923ea157e9d2947224f4f83f33422","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff515545459e2ced523e94a8f7b39b640e33a671","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c7e84eb20a75d1fb4d764d51242045c5d8c60c9","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e798671b49a080e25eaece3109df2a3670b0f34","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8fe7f10501c9ffc18ce63e0e76dbddbbf902f69","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3a56cf1edcb85c868703b694ed4d15c405d6391","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd4cfb48881db7e7530921cf3b8883e7fa8e86a7","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8222ec4567c53e456cd8cb0be3d33fbeafee7ec","tid":1017086,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2dd1994b184b7c222a015123169a0008bd4daf0","tid":1017086,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}